-- U.S. Sues Amazon.com, Macy’s Over Alleged Textile Mislabeling
-- B y   T o m   S c h o e n b e r g
-- 2013-01-03T15:39:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-03/u-s-sues-amazon-com-macy-s-over-alleged-textile-mislabeling.html
Amazon.com Inc. (AMZN)  and  Macy’s Inc. (M)  were
sued by the U.S. Federal Trade Commission over claims the
retailers misled consumers with claims that fabrics they sold
were made of bamboo fiber, according to lawsuits filed in
federal court in Washington.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Tom Schoenberg in Washington at 
 tschoenberg@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Fred Strasser at 
 fstrasser@bloomberg.net  